# Support Ticket System

A full-stack ticket management system with AI-powered categorization.

## Built

- **Backend**: Django + DRF + PostgreSQL
- **Frontend**: React
- **LLM**: OpenAI GPT-3.5 for auto-suggesting category/priority
- **Docker**: Full containerization

## Features

✅ Submit tickets with AI suggestions (category/priority auto-filled based on description)
✅ Override AI suggestions manually before submitting
✅ View all tickets with filters (category, priority, status) and search
✅ Update ticket status inline
✅ Stats dashboard with real-time metrics
✅ Fully containerized - runs with one command

## API Endpoints

- `POST /api/tickets/` - Create ticket
- `GET /api/tickets/` - List tickets (filters: ?category=&priority=&status=&search=)
- `PATCH /api/tickets/<id>/` - Update ticket
- `GET /api/tickets/stats/` - Aggregated metrics
- `POST /api/tickets/classify/` - LLM suggestion endpoint

## LLM Integration

- **Model**: OpenAI GPT-3.5-turbo
- **Prompt**: f"""
        Given this support ticket description, classify it into:
        - Category: billing, technical, account, or general
        - Priority: low, medium, high, or critical

        Description: "{description}"

        Return ONLY JSON format: {{"category": "...", "priority": "..."}}
        """
